    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Digital Eulogy</h2><br>John's Tombstone is a narrative game with 3 chapters each one completely different from the other. You will be driving a car in a dream, walking around on the afterlife and talking with angels to unravel a story of acceptance, sci-fi and emotional strength. The chapters here within will resonate more if you've lost someone dear to you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826820/extras/92809a36bd03e29fe7004672f3dd647b.poster.avif?t=1650394959\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826820/extras/92809a36bd03e29fe7004672f3dd647b.webm?t=1650394959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826820/extras/92809a36bd03e29fe7004672f3dd647b.mp4?t=1650394959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Three Stories</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A sci-fi, mindbending, emotional experience.<br></li><li>3 stories tied by one unique arc<br></li><li>A mix of 3D and 2D with different mechanics on each chapter<br></li><li>A walking simulator experience, lots of dialogues written with wit and love<br></li><li>Discover the afterlife, the realm of dreams and much more!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826820/extras/8cd938d059df60acad34d3ebdcd1a8bf.poster.avif?t=1650394959\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826820/extras/8cd938d059df60acad34d3ebdcd1a8bf.webm?t=1650394959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826820/extras/8cd938d059df60acad34d3ebdcd1a8bf.mp4?t=1650394959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't miss our demo!</h2><br>Want to take a glimpse before the dive? Check out our free demo! It includes the Prologue and Chapter 1.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Something different</h2><br>This game is the digital eulogy to my dad, a man whose name was not John. Each chapter will tell you a bit of how people fight with grief while giving you some good sci-fi, a thing that John really loved.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826820/extras/8defb699a893c426a13bb88377bf900b.poster.avif?t=1650394959\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826820/extras/8defb699a893c426a13bb88377bf900b.webm?t=1650394959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826820/extras/8defb699a893c426a13bb88377bf900b.mp4?t=1650394959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
